text: Wow, that's a lot of books.

I borrowed all the books I was interested
in from the university library.

I also stopped by the bookstore and bought
some new releases, so it got even heavier.

You just finished a live, and now
you're studying... Impressive.
Oh, it's because the live is over, right?

Lately, I've been focusing on building my body,
so now I need to absorb knowledge.

Time doesn't stop,
so I can't stand still either!
